citta the next one the citta is more to do with your mental states your total mental states and the fourth category is the dhamma which actually refers to investigating all these three from certain points of view so when something something unwholesome comes up then we look at them from the point of view of the hindrances

79
00:07:14,225 --> 00:07:22,012
When we look at the body and the congregation of factors that make up a human being, we look at these aggregates.

