113
00:09:30,645 --> 00:09:32,708
That's not mystical or magical.

114
00:09:33,048 --> 00:09:36,114
You just know that the breath has come to an end and there's a stop.

115
00:09:36,134 --> 00:09:36,615
It's finished.

116
00:09:37,076 --> 00:09:38,076
Then the next breath comes.

117
00:09:38,597 --> 00:09:41,361
So you're constantly aware of the beginning and ending of things.

118
00:09:41,522 --> 00:09:45,207
That's the radical impermanence that we live with.

119
00:09:50,892 --> 00:10:02,171
