00:17:00,427 --> 00:17:02,289
You can't do anything without trust, can you?

203
00:17:02,530 --> 00:17:08,077
I mean, if you go on a high diving board and if you don't trust yourself to do it, you won't do it, will you?

204
00:17:08,097 --> 00:17:09,118
