00:40:11,853 --> 00:40:11,932
Hmm.

509
00:40:11,952 --> 00:40:17,360
So now, can you... You know, this is a reflection that you can bring up tomorrow when we...

510
00:40:17,577 --> 00:40:20,159
Do a little bit of reflection about our lives.

511
00:40:20,539 --> 00:40:22,862
Have you ever been so engaged in your life in anything?

512
00:40:23,043 --> 00:40:30,570
Have you ever been so engaged that it's drawn every last ounce of your commitment to it, you see?

513
00:40:32,092 --> 00:40:41,423
Now, you can see that this is not only important in what we do, in anything you want to achieve, but spiritually speaking, it's a must.

514
00:40:42,744 --> 00:40:43,686
Can't be half-hearted.

515
00:40:45,960 --> 00:40:48,623
So that's why I was bringing up these four magical paths.

